      <title>礼来减肥药在中国获批，与诺和诺德竞争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/lilly-s-weight-loss-drug-approved-in-china-amid-race-with-novo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在诺和诺德公司 (Novo Nordisk A/S) 推出类似疗法后不到一个月，礼来公司的 Mounjaro 就获得了中国监管机构的减肥批准，这加剧了中国这个全球肥胖问题最严重国家之间的竞争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/lilly-s-weight-loss-drug-approved-in-china-amid-race-with-novo</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 10:05:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>塞尔维亚获得欧盟供应协议，推进锂业发展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/serbia-secures-eu-supply-deal-as-advances-lithium-ambitions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塞尔维亚与欧盟签署了一项提供关键原材料的框架协议，这个巴尔干国家寻求利用计划中的锂矿成为电动汽车生产的区域中心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/serbia-secures-eu-supply-deal-as-advances-lithium-ambitions</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 09:57:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国全国人大三次会议结果令人失望，铜价或创 2022 年以来最差一周</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/copper-set-for-worst-week-since-2022-as-china-plenum-disappoints</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中国政策会议未能提出更多刺激措施来支撑金属需求，铜价创下 2022 年以来最大单周跌幅，铁矿石价格延续跌势，跌向每吨 100 美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/copper-set-for-worst-week-since-2022-as-china-plenum-disappoints</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 03:09:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>科技中断对企业造成冲击，股市陷入困境：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于全球计算机系统故障影响到旅游、交易和支持服务，全球股市周五陷入困境，并有可能加剧科技股的回调。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 22:41:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>远洋集团债务计划获支持，但仍面临阻力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/sino-ocean-says-some-lenders-back-debt-restructuring-proposal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[违约的建筑商远洋集团控股有限公司正在努力争取足够的支持，以使其债务重组计划获得批准，但由于主要债券持有人团体的反对，仍远远未达到所需的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/sino-ocean-says-some-lenders-back-debt-restructuring-proposal</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 17:10:56 GMT</pubDate>
